.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第二十二条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">相关单位应加强对侵害未成年人案件强制报告的政策</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">和法治</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">宣传，强化全社会保护未成年人、与侵害未成年人违法犯罪行为作斗争的意识，争取理解与支持，营造良好社会氛围。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第二十三条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">本意见自印发之日起试行。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\\\'DejaVu Sans\\\';font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'editer\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'\',\n  \'views\' => \'\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'html\' => \'1\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'config\' => \n  array (\n    \'allow_ip\' => \n    array (\n      \'enabled\' => \'0\',\n      \'collectip\' => \'\',\n      \'beginip\' => \'\',\n      \'endip\' => \'\',\n      \'ruleoutip\' => \'\',\n    ),\n  ),\n  \'custom_a\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'credit_type\' => \'0\',\n  \'credit\' => \'1\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'bec8db1bd5332eff\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'ycyyo\',\n)','1652842834');
INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` VALUES ('5709','0','cms','item','update','3270','883','','ycyyo','修改内容 | 关于建立侵害未成年人案件强制报告制度的意见（试行）','/index.php/cms/item-list-category-883-page-4','10.10.20.14','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-update?model=article&id=3270&verified=1\',\n  \'cid\' => \'883\',\n  \'title\' => \'关于建立侵害未成年人案件强制报告制度的意见（试行）\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2022-05-18 11:00:34\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'\',\n  \'level_time\' => \'不选则永久有效\',\n  \'level\' => \'\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'thumb_width\' => \'328\',\n  \'thumb_height\' => \'247\',\n  \'summary\' => \'关于建立侵害未成年人案件强制报告制度的意见（试行）第一条为切实加强对未成年人的全面综合司法保护，及时有效惩治侵害未成年人违法犯罪，根据《中华人民共和国刑事诉讼法》《中华人民共和国未成年人保护法》《中华人民共和国反家庭暴力法》《中华人民共和国执业医师法\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'verify_frame\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-indent:64.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:4.0000;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:30.0000pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第一条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">为切实加强对未成年人的全面综合司法保护，及时有效惩治侵害未成年人违法犯罪，根据</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">《中华人民共和国刑事诉讼法》《中华人民共和国未成年人保护法》《中华人民共和国反家庭暴力法》《中华人民共和国执业医师法》</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">及相关法律法规，结合未成年人保护工作实际，制定本意见。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第二条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">侵害未成年人案件</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">强制报告，是指</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,0);mso-highlight:rgb(255,255,0);\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">国家机关、法律法规授权行使公权力的各类组织及法律规定的公职人员，密切接触未成年人行业的各类组织及其从业人员</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">，在工作中发现未成年人遭受或者疑似遭受不法侵害以及面临不法侵害</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">危险的，应当立即向公安机关报案或举报。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第三条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">本意见所称</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">密切接触</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">未</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">成年人</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">行业的各类组织，是指依法对未成年人负有</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">教育、看护、医疗、救助、监护等特殊职责</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">，</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">或者虽不负有特殊职责但具有</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">密切接触未成年人条件</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">的企事业单位、基层群众自治组织、社会组织。主要包括：居（村）民委员会；中小学校、幼儿园、校外培训机构、未成年人校外活动场所等教育机构及校车服务提供者；托儿所等托育服务机构；</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">医院、妇幼保健院、急救中心、诊所等医疗机构</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">；儿童福利机构、救助管理机构、未成年人救助保护机构、社会工作服务机构；旅店、宾馆等。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第四条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">本意见所称在工作中发现未成年人遭受或者疑似遭受不法侵害以及面临不法侵害危险的情况包括：</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（一）未成年人的</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">生殖器官或隐私部位遭受或疑似遭受非正常损伤</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">的；</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（二）</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">不满十四周岁的女性未成年人遭受或疑似遭受性侵害、怀孕、流产的</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">；</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（三）</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">十四周岁以上女性未成年人遭受或疑似遭受性侵害所致怀孕、流产</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">的；</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（四）未成年人身体存在多处损伤、严重营养不良、意识不清，</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">存在或疑似存在受到家庭暴力、欺凌、虐待、殴打或者被人麻醉</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">等情形的；</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（五）未成年人因自杀、自残、工伤、中毒、被人麻醉、殴打等非正常原因导致伤残、死亡情形的；</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">六</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">）未成年人被遗弃或长期处于无人照料状态</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">的</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">；</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">七</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">）</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">发现未成年人来源不明、失踪或者被拐卖、收买的；</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">八</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">）</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">发现未成年人被组织乞讨的；</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（九）</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">其他严重侵害未成年人身心健康的情形或未成年人正在</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">面临不法侵害</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">危险的。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第五条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">根据本意见规定情形向公安机关报案或举报的，应</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">按照主管行政机关要求报告备案</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第六条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">具备先期核实条件的相关单位、机构、组织及人员，</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">可以</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">对未成年人疑似遭受不法侵害的情况进行</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">初步核实</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">，并在报案或举报时将</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">相关材料一并提交公安机关</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第七条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">医疗机构及其从业人员在收治遭受或疑似遭受人身、精神损害的未成年人时，应当保持高度警惕，</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">按规定书写、记录和保存相关病历资料</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第八条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">公安机关接到疑似侵害未成年人权益的报案或举报后，应当立即接受，问明案件初步情况，并制作笔录。根据案件的具体情况，涉嫌违反治安管理的，依法受案审查；涉嫌犯罪的，依法立案侦查。对不属于自己管辖的，及时移送有管辖权的公安机关。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第九条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">公安机关侦查未成年人被侵害案件，应当依照法定程序，及时、全面收集固定证据。对于</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">严重侵害未成年人的暴力犯罪案件、社会高度关注的重大、敏感案件，</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">公安机关、人民检察院应当加强办案中的协商、沟通与配合</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">公安机关、人民检察院</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">依法</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">向报案人员或者单位调取指控犯罪所需要的处理记录、监控资料、证人证言等证据时，相关单位及其工作人员应当积极予以协助配合，并按照有关规定全面提供。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第十条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">公安机关应当在受案或者立案后三日内向报案单位反馈案件进展，并在移送审查起诉前告知报案单位</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第十一条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">人民检察院应当切实加强对侵害未成年人案件的立案监督。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">认为</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">公安机关应当立案而不立案的，应当要求公安机关说明不立案的理由。认为不立案理由不能成立的，应当通知公安机关立案，公安机关接到通知后应当立即立案。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第十二条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">公</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">安机关、人民检察院发现未成年人需要保护救助的，应当</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">委托或者</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">联合民政部门</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">或共青团、</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">妇联</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">等群团</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">组织，</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">对未成年人及其家庭实施必要的经济救助、医疗救治、心理干预、调查评估等保护措施。未成年被害人生活特别困难的，司法机关应当及时启动司法救助。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">公安机关、人民检察院发现未成年人父母或者其他监护人不依法履行监护职责，或者侵害未成年人合法权益的，应当予以训诫或者责令其接受家庭教育指导。经教育仍不改正，</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">情节严重的，应当依法依规予以惩处。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">公安机关、妇联、居民委员会、村民委员会、救助管理机构、未成年人救助保护机构发现未成年人遭受家庭暴力或面临家庭暴力的现实危险，可以依法向人民法院代为申请人身安全保护令。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第十三条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">公安机关、人民检察院和司法行政机关及教育、民政、卫生健康</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">等</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">主管行政机关应当对报案人的信息予以保密</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">。违法窃取、泄露报告事项、报告受理情况以及报告人信息的，依法依规予以严惩。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第十四条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">相关单位</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">、组织</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">及其工作人员应当注</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">意</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">保护未成年人隐私，对于涉案未成年人身份、案情等信息资料予以严格保密，严禁通过</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">互联网</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">或者以其他方式进行传播</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">私自传播的，依法给予治安处罚或追究其刑事责任。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第十五条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'DejaVu Sans\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">依法保障相关单位及其工作人员履行强制报告责任，对根据规定报告侵害未成年人案件而引发的纠纷，报告人不予承担相应法律责任；对于</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'DejaVu Sans\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">干扰、阻碍报告的组织或个人，依法追究法律责任</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'DejaVu Sans\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第十六条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">负有报告义务的单位及其工作人员</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">未履行报告职责，造成严重后果的，由其主管行政机关或者本单位依法对直接负责的主管人员或者其他直接责任人员给予相应处分</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">；构成犯罪的，依法追究刑事责任。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\ntext-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">相关单位或者单位主管人员阻止工作人员报告的，予以从重处罚</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第十七条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">对于行使公权力的公职人员长期不重视强制报告工作，不按规定落实强制报告制度要求的，根据其情节、后果等情况，监察委员会应当依法对相关单位和失职失责人员进行问责，对涉嫌职务违法犯罪的依法调查处理。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第十八条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">人民检察院依法对本意见的执行情况进行法律监督。对于工作中发现相关单位对本意见执行、监管不力的，可以通过</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">发出</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">检察建议书等方式</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">进行</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">监督</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">纠正。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第十九条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">对于因及时</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">报案使遭受侵害未成年人得到妥善保护、犯罪分子受到依法惩处的</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">，公安机关、人民检察院</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">、民政部门</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">应及时向其</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">主管部门</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">反馈相关情况，</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">单独或联合给予相关机构、人员奖励、表彰</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第二十条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">强制报告责任单位的主管部门应当在本部门职能范围内指导、督促责任单位严格落实本意见，并通过年度报告、不定期巡查等方式，对本意见执行情况进行检查。注重加强指导和培训，切实提高</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">相关单位和人员的</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">未成年人保护意识和能力水平。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第二十一条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">各级监察委员会、</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">人民检察院、公安机关</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">、</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">司法行政机关</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">、</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">教育、民政、卫生健康部门</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">和妇联、共青团组织</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">应当</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">加强沟通</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">交流，定期通报工作情况，</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">及时</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">研究实践中出现的新情况、新问题。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">各部门</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">建立联席会议制度，明确强制报告工作联系人，畅通联系渠道，加强工作衔接和信息共享。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">人民检察院负责联席会议制度日常工作安排。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第二十二条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">相关单位应加强对侵害未成年人案件强制报告的政策</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-bidi-font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">和法治</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\';mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">宣传，强化全社会保护未成年人、与侵害未成年人违法犯罪行为作斗争的意识，争取理解与支持，营造良好社会氛围。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">第二十三条</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\\\'yes\\\';font-family:黑体;